},{"pid":"22930db9a5bd380529a17c4fdf3308d03abaa18f","tid":326240,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:25:24.000Z","msg":"一陣仲要去大埔見客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人知果邊水浸未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d726e80c0598cec69b11fd54f4ad5a2439424c3","tid":326240,"uid":59865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>局部大雨報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔區 70mm以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對面海 馬鞍山都水浸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8點出門口嗰陣馬鞍山真係大雨到仆街</blockquote><br />\n拎半日睇下點再算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老母行少少路都成身濕晒 莫講我要番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a447a030a3bdadb1e9589e2a086f13a7dbfed973","tid":326240,"uid":28422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"新界西既朋友真係要感恩<br />\n唔洗濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c0a3de4f43346c9002e64558042d754ed00f5e","tid":326240,"uid":122233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一陣仲要去大埔見客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人知果邊水浸未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大埔邊度先"},{"pid":"6fd2948d08460788964f587bb4d8c26e91ba9c0c","tid":326240,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:18:29.000Z","msg":"西貢大雨到絕望,有d位水浸封埋路"},{"pid":"b1534b16624df78093e64ac8bf1d274589924434","tid":326240,"uid":83373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>EC連續幾報都對報出有子彈颱<br />\n暫時預登陸點為雷州半島至珠西一帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n+120以後都係睇定d先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX 2 <br />\n可能聽日就調没呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係7月23，五年喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c3cffa1073ca57ab6cac13d474ff920b8b57d3","tid":326240,"uid":59865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T02:37:13.000Z","msg":"而家馬鞍山又停晒雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩先老世話其他區同事都番到公司點解你番唔到<br />\n但成間公司得我一個係住新界北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e2d66b0cbb0da06ffe3c5061eb67b2745e7fc5","tid":326240,"uid":123583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"最新歐中、NCEP GFS都預測而家係菲律賓南部既廣闊雲團將會有所發展，向西北偏北移動，星期六日相當接近本港<br />\n<br />\n大範圍既流場顯示，而家影響緊我地既高空槽會逐漸減弱同離開，未來兩三日副高將會北跳，因此預計呢個低壓區會受副高引導大致向西北移動，星期六最接近沿岸地區。但過去幾報預測尚未穩定落黎，登陸點仍然有好大變數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時NCEP GFS比較支持菲律賓以東既低壓區發展，未來預測仍有可能有大變化<br />\n<br />\n左: 歐中，右: NCEP GFS<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/143246_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F143246_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=900bb88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/143249_df7579df015dd85139a4196cf3446694.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F143249_df7579df015dd85139a4196cf3446694.PNG&h=3b5703a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b3a538b725d042b9a3b4c14089c90816e016054","tid":326240,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zt5c6e73\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzt5c6e73&h=4f1e32fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想合體？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2aa77c3ebf3d400c5226be2543aa5ebdefe0c3","tid":326240,"uid":127768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"啲紅色上緊嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebf9b70a035b902ba2f97f0dae4441d36fcf24e","tid":326240,"uid":35219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:55:41.000Z","msg":"今朝新東而家到新西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bf8359ecb656e2bc735e3256658622f362d1f8","tid":326240,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:07:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最新歐中、NCEP GFS都預測而家係菲律賓南部既廣闊雲團將會有所發展，向西北偏北移動，星期六日相當接近本港<br />\n<br />\n大範圍既流場顯示，而家影響緊我地既高空槽會逐漸減弱同離開，未來兩三日副高將會北跳，因此預計呢個低壓區會受副高引導大致向西北移動，星期六最接近沿岸地區。但過去幾報預測尚未穩定落黎，登陸點仍然有好大變數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時NCEP GFS比較支持菲律賓以東既低壓區發展，未來預測仍有可能有大變化<br />\n<br />\n左: 歐中，右: NCEP GFS<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/143246_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F143246_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=900bb88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/143249_df7579df015dd85139a4196cf3446694.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net